data.description: From 316- Go south on Harbins Rd., then turn right onto New Hope Rd. After 2.9 miles, Windsor Knoll will be on the right.    This craftsman style single story home has plenty of curb appeal! Luxury vinyl plank floors throughout main living areas. Jack and Jill bath. Oversized formal dining room with tray ceiling. Butlers pantry, walk in pantry, and gourmet kitchen. Open concept living areas. Covered back patio. Spacious master suite with tray ceiling, luxury walk in tiled shower and separate vanities in master bathroom. This home is a must see
